17 Aug 2015 Deputy Minister of Communications Stella Ndabeni-Abrahams to deliver the Keynote address at the Soweto TV s Premiere Graduation CeremonyDeputy Minister of Communications Stella Ndabeni Abrahams will deliver a keynote address at the Soweto TV s premiere graduation ceremony. The recipients of this souvenir are 136 young people who have undergone training and successfully completed the station s learnership programme.Soweto TV is proud to be the first community broadcasting channel to run a successful and accredited learnership programme. Soweto TV regards this achievement as a significant milestone and are grateful and honoured to be joined by the Deputy Minister of Communications in celebrating this joyous occasion.Members of the media are invited as follows: Date: Tuesday, 18th August 2015 Time: 17h00 Venue: Soweto Theatre, Cnr Bolani Link and Bolani Rd, Jabulani, Soweto RSVPs: Senzeni Ngubane 060 647 6705 senzi@doc.gov.za Media enquiries: Mzimasi Ngqelu Contact: 0769043557 Email: mzi@doc.gov.za Issued by Government Communications (GCIS) on behalf of the Ministry of Communications